- **“You”** means the individual or legal entity exercising permissions under this License.
- **“Commercial Entity”** means any organization or individual using the Software for business or revenue-generating purposes.
- **“Gross Annual Revenue”** means total worldwide revenue before expenses, calculated for the most recent fiscal year.

