## 3. Qualified Free Use

You may use the Software **free of charge** if you meet **any** of the following criteria:

### a) Individuals
You are using the Software for personal, educational, or hobby purposes.

### b) Non-Profit Organizations
You are a legally registered non-profit organization using the Software in furtherance of non-profit activities.

### c) Small Businesses
You are a Commercial Entity with **Gross Annual Revenue less than USD $100,000 (or equivalent in local currency)** in the most recent fiscal year.

Currency equivalence shall be determined using the average annual exchange rate for that fiscal year.

